query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('adapter',
'bit-manipulation',
'filtering',
'google-cloud-datastore',
'ionic2',
'jasper-reports',
'lapply',
'latex',
'material-ui',
'nsmutablearray',
'observable',
'qt5',
'rotation',
'user-input',
'wxpython');
